telegraf
========

Role variables
==============

telegraf_outputs_influxdb_url
-----------------------------

Required


telegraf_snmp_enabled
---------------------

Boolean which defaults to no.


telegraf_snmp_agents
--------------------

List of IP[:PORT] SNMP agents. Defaults to [ "127.0.0.1:161"Â ].


telegraf_snmp_community
-----------------------

Defaults to "public".


Exim
====

There are test files in the tests directory. exim.conf is a Telegraf
configuration for testing Exim mainlog patterns. Simply use it like this:

  telegraf --config exim.conf

You should see as many <= as => lines.


SNMP
====

Hosts configured for SNMP monitoring must have the non-free repository
components. This is done by setting the common_deb_sources_components
variable and running the base.yml playbook.

  common_deb_sources_components: main non-free

References:
  https://www.dev-eth0.de/blog/2016/12/06/grafana_snmp.html
  https://wiki.debian.org/SNMP
  http://www.net-snmp.org/docs/mibs/ifMIBObjects.html


